title: Blue Fire Flame Rubberized Snap on Protective Cover Case for Samsung Galaxy Reverb M950
description: Protect and personalize your cell phone with this Rubberized Shield Protector Case. Shield Protector Case is a set of form fitting snap-on cover that protect your cell phone without adding a lot of bulk. Shield Protector Case has openings for camera, volume/side buttons, charger jack and speakers which allows access to all phone functions. Easy snap-on installation
